 sea nation, the people live in communi\u00ad ties that are built on groups of these POK\u00e9MON."},{"version":"crystal","text":"The points on its head absorb nutrients from clean water. They cannot survive in polluted water."},{"version":"ruby","text":"CORSOLA\u2019s branches glitter very beautifully in seven colors when they catch sunlight. If any branch breaks off, this POK\u00e9MON grows it back in just one night."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"Clusters of CORSOLA congregate in warm seas where they serve as ideal hiding places for smaller POK\u00e9MON. When the water temperature falls, this POK\u00e9MON migrates to the southern seas."},{"version":"emerald","text":"CORSOLA live in warm southern seas. If the sea becomes polluted, the beautiful coral stalks become discolored and crumble away in tatters."},{"version":"firered","text":"In a south sea nation, the people live in communities that are built on groups of these POK\u00e9MON."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure for its beauty."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Many live in the clean seas of the south. They apparently can\u2019t live in polluted waters."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Many live in the clean seas of the south. They apparently can\u2019t live in polluted waters."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Many live in the clean seas of the south. They apparently can\u2019t live in polluted waters."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure because of its beauty."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"In a south-sea nation, the people live in communities that are built on groups of these Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"black","text":"Many live in the clean seas of the south. They apparently can\u2019t live in polluted waters."},{"version":"white","text":"Many live in the clean seas of the south. They apparently can\u2019t live in polluted waters."},{"version":"black-2","text":"The